fm: bool hasPathSum(TreeNode* root, int targetSum) {     if (root == NULL) {       return false;     }     if (root->val == targetSum && root->right == NULL && root->left == NULL) {       return true;     }     return hasPathSum(root->left, targetSum - root->val) ||            hasPathSum(root->right, targetSum - root->val);   }

fm: int maxProfit(vector<int>& prices) {     int profit = 0, price = INT_MAX;     for (int i = 0; i < prices.size(); i++) {       price = min(price, prices[i]);       int present_profit = prices[i] - price;       profit = max(present_profit, profit);     }     return profit;   }

fm: bool isMatch(string str, string pattern) {     int m = pattern.size();     int n = str.size();      bool dp[n + 1][m + 1];     for (int i = 0; i < n + 1; i++) {       for (int j = 0; j < m + 1; j++) {         dp[i][j] = false;       }     }     dp[0][0] = true;      for (int i = 1; i <= m; i++) {       if (pattern[i - 1] == '*') dp[0][i] = dp[0][i - 1];     }     for (int i = 1; i < n + 1; i++) {       for (int j = 1; j < m + 1; j++) {         if (str[i - 1] == pattern[j - 1] || pattern[j - 1] == '?')           dp[i][j] = dp[i - 1][j - 1];         else if (pattern[j - 1] == '*')           dp[i][j] = dp[i - 1][j] || dp[i][j - 1];       }     }     return dp[n][m];   }

fm: int maxSubArray(vector<int>& nums) {     int cur = 0, mx = INT_MIN, n = nums.size();      for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {       cur += nums[i];       mx = max(mx, cur);       if (cur < 0) {         cur = 0;       }     }     return mx;   }
